Author: BEDBulimic
Text: Yup absolutely normal, your muscles are holding onto that water to heal itself.  Fitness models will go ham with exercise and pushups before a photoshoot so they look more “swole” for the pics but is it fat? NOPE it is water and lies.   Their fake extra swole muscles don’t stay forever, and once your body is done repairing your muscles, it’ll pee out the remainder. You’ll be alright love 💛
